      "message": "discussed offline, going to keep basic structure, but changing the comment.\n\nSummary: Bots and users deal with the checkouts in terms of filesystem layout. Working with either of these other proposed formats (e.g. for calculating Diff, displaying in HTML) is very awkward, and almost always requires an intermediate format like what this proto has now.",
      "parentUuid": "0f6ca285_aaf924e6",
      "range": {
